<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{ shop.name }} - W-ALEX</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600&display=swap');

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        background-image: url({{ 'lion-background.jpg.png' | asset_url }});
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        color: #C19C4B;
      }

      .overlay {
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 2rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 600px;
      }

      footer {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="overlay">
      <h1>W-ALEX</h1>
      <p>More than style — it's a symbol of power, elegance and legacy. Designed for the elite. Built to endure.</p>
      <footer>BEYOND LIMITS · Crafted for Entrepreneurs</footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
